## Case 1: Chaining Transformations (The "Pipe" model)
$input |> __("lowercase") |> !! |> __("capitalize");

## Case 2: Formula Calls (Standard and Symbol-based)
my_math(1, 2, a: 3);
__(42, "string", [ 1, 2, 3 ]);
!!(5, 10);
$$("string_ops");

## Case 3: Dispatch with Snatches and Catches
my_data [ $id ] {
    $id !!!
    //info !
} ( a: 1, b: 2 );

## Case 4: Brace Formulas and Relational Ops
> (10);
>= (20);
>> (!!(5));
